Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:00.97,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Fallin' fallin' love now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:06.48,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}這就是命中注定…Oh my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:14.15,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不會讓你說你沒聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.65,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}1,2…heart beat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:19.49,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在星辰大海中唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.99,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只屬於我的命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:26.45,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}若是動了真情  怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:25.45,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(你又會)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:29.37,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用盡全心全意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.71,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去尋找未來的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:40.55,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在你那裡找到了  不會消去的夢之所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:46.39,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}假如世界停轉一天的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.77,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(在停轉之時)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:53.86,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}請一直一直抱緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:53.86,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(緊緊抱著我)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:57.07,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}盡想著這些任性的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:00.82,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}對不起…喜歡你「沒有極限」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:04.74,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不要害怕  明天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.12,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(1,2 heart!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:05.53,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(1,2 beat!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.00,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}希望可以確認你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:08.75,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(UN-DELAYED)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:16.34,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用觸及的指尖接受我熱情的奇蹟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.34,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Oh my love!
